title: Google Cyberfraud Case Study
description: Case Study: Discover how Jayson Hunter helped create a working prototype for Google's 'Ad Traffic Quality Resource Center' website.

caseStudyDetails.projectDescription: Beyond, a design and technology ideas company based in London Bridge, had a requirement from one of their clients in San Francisco, to produce new designs for their 'Ad Traffic Quality Resource Center' website. That client was non other than Google.
